SRMA - short read micro re-aligner 

=== To Install ===

1. Move into the c-code sub-directory.

2.a Download the latest samtools from http://samtools.sf.net 
and rename the directory to 'samtools' (no quotes).

2.b Move into the 'samtools' directory and type 'make' 
(no quotes), then move back up to the c-code directory.

3. Run:
 sh autogen.sh && ./configure && make

=== For more help ===

see http://srma.sf.net
